On the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]], the '''cloudsea''' was the collective term for the [[Poison/Legends|poisonous]], heavier-than-[[Atmosphere/Legends|air]] gases that fell to the planet's lower areas. It covered most of the planet, with the exception of the [[Korunnal Highland]], the only habitable area because it was above the level of the cloudsea.

